Num Block Puzzle - Brick Break is a fascinating puzzle game with addictive gameplay.

Num Block Puzzle - Brick Break is very simple, but has a wealth of skills and game strategies.

In this game, your task is to exchange adjacent digital lattices. After the lattices are exchanged, if there are more than three adjacent numbers, they will be merged into one number and the number will be added to the result of the original number.

Merge as many numbers as possible and get higher scores.

No time limit, no tense battles, enjoy pure entertainment digital games~

